alls (approx. 1 tablespoon each) and place into Varoma dish and onto Varoma tray. Set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"content":"Place remaining 500 g water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b> or until balls are cooked through."},{"content":"Transfer strained yoghurt into a small bowl. Add reserved parsley mixture, season with salt and pepper and stir to combine. Serve fish balls immediately. "}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can use any type of firm white fish fillet such as barramundi, snapper or ling in this recipe.<br>","For a different flavour, try replacing the parsley with tarragon or coriander.","For a more complete meal, serve with a fresh green salad. <br>"],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 50m","4 portions"]}